      "message": "[warning] Line 1498: This unconditionally indexes `pluginData[\"bodyOverwrite\"]`, so creating an edition for a message that has not been translated yet mutates `pluginData` by inserting an empty overwrite and exposes an empty `bodyOverwrite` field in the edition history. It can also make later missing-overwrite scans think the original already has overwrite data. Only copy the field when it exists.\\n```suggestion\\n                if (const auto boIt \u003d it-\u003esecond-\u003epluginData.find(\"bodyOverwrite\");\\n                    boIt !\u003d it-\u003esecond-\u003epluginData.end()) {\\n                    it-\u003esecond-\u003eeditions.front()[\"bodyOverwrite\"] \u003d boIt-\u003esecond;\\n                }\\n```",
